 dust heated by stars is not\nalways associated with young stars, and that the IR emission from M51b is\nprimarily powered by stars older than 5 Gyr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Oct 2017 18:10:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-20"}
