ow that particularly stable anion sites result when triangular\narrangements of silanol groups enable multiple hydrogen bonds with the various\nfluorine atoms of a given anion, elucidating an important trapping mechanism at\nthe silica surface.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 07:18:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-27"}
