 understand the weak or quiescent activities\nin supermassive black-hole systems. Further simultaneous millimeter and X-ray\nmonitoring of this kind of LLAGNs will help us to better understand the\nphysical origin of multiwaveband emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 08:44:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2018 01:18:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-21"}
