\nangles for the CIR ($\\beta \\geq 35^{\\circ}$) were found to best reproduce the\ntype of spectroscopic variability reported in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 14:16:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
